  "description": {
   "en": "An authentic fantasy about Chesuka, a linguistic genius, and Siki, a beautiful prince of an oppressed people. In this world ruled by people who use “supernatural powers (lua)” given by God, people without powers are called “yagyu” and are subjected to discrimination. At the Makali Academy of the Republic of Nankan, where many children of royalty and rulers from around the world attend, it is a tradition to elect members of the student council, especially those of the most exalted status. The Yagoo prince Siki enters the school. \n\nChesuka, who is in charge of interpretation in the student council, deepens her interaction with Shiki as his interpreter.",
   "ja": "神より与えられた超能力（ルア）を使役する人々に支配されている世界で、その力を持たない人々は『ヤグー』と呼ばれ過酷な差別に晒されていた。そんなある日、世界中の王族・為政者の子供たちが通うナンカン共和国のマカリ学園にヤグーの王子が入学することになる。それをきっかけに世界は一変し――…!? 言語学の天才である少女・チェスカと虐げられし民も美しき王子・シキが出会う時、世界のルールは覆される!!"
  },
